import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  Form,
  Input,
  Button,
  Radio,
  Select,
  Cascader,
  DatePicker,
  InputNumber,
  TreeSelect,
  Switch,
  Alert,
  Row,
  Col,
} from "antd";

const Addlisting = () => {
  const [componentSize, setComponentSize] = useState("default");

  const onFormLayoutChange = ({ size }) => {
    setComponentSize(size);
  };

  return (
    <>
      <Alert message="PROPERTY TYPE AND LOCATION" type="success" />
      <Form
        labelCol={{
          span: 4,
        }}
        wrapperCol={{
          span: 14,
        }}
        layout="horizontal"
        initialValues={{
          size: componentSize,
        }}
        onValuesChange={onFormLayoutChange}
        size={componentSize}
      >
        <Form.Item label="Form Size" name="size">
          <Radio.Group>
            <Radio.Button value="small">Sale</Radio.Button>
            <Radio.Button value="default">Rent</Radio.Button>
          </Radio.Group>
        </Form.Item>

        <Form.Item label="Form Size" name="size">
          <Radio.Group>
            <Radio.Button value="home">Homes</Radio.Button>
            <Radio.Button value="plots">Plots</Radio.Button>
            <Radio.Button value="commercial">Commercial</Radio.Button>
          </Radio.Group>
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="Select city">
          <Select>
            <Select.Option value="demo" selected>
              Islamabad
            </Select.Option>
            <Select.Option value="demo">Rawalpindi</Select.Option>
            <Select.Option value="demo">Karachi</Select.Option>
          </Select>
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="Location">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>

        <Form.Item label="TreeSelect">
          <TreeSelect
            treeData={[
              {
                title: "Light",
                value: "light",
                children: [
                  {
                    title: "Bamboo",
                    value: "bamboo",
                  },
                ],
              },
            ]}
          />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="Cascader">
          <Cascader
            options={[
              {
                value: "zhejiang",
                label: "Zhejiang",
                children: [
                  {
                    value: "hangzhou",
                    label: "Hangzhou",
                  },
                ],
              },
            ]}
          />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="DatePicker">
          <DatePicker />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="InputNumber">
          <InputNumber />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="Switch">
          <Switch />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item label="Button">
          <Button>Button</Button>
        </Form.Item>
      </Form>

      <Alert message="PROPERTY DETAILS" type="success" />
      <Form.Item label="Property Title">
        <Input />
      </Form.Item>

      <Form.Item label="Property Details">
        <Input />
      </Form.Item>

      <Form.Item label="All inclusive Price">
        <Input />
      </Form.Item>

      <Row>
        <Col lg={12}>
          <Form.Item label="Land Area">
            <Input />
          </Form.Item>
        </Col>
        <Col lg={12}>
          <Form.Item label="Square feet">
            <Select>
              <Select.Option value="1" selected>
                1
              </Select.Option>
              <Select.Option value="2">2</Select.Option>
              <Select.Option value="2">3</Select.Option>
            </Select>
          </Form.Item>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
};

export default Addlisting;
